				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You'll never have an end-all solution that covers everything. The best you can do is have a dual approach: self-contained format(s) for describing new games, and a database of known games. The former allows a determined person to make a game work. The latter accounts for all the existing files out there to make them work without having to convert them to a &quot;correct&quot; format.</div>

